WEBVTT

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:34.960
fonio has a delicious,
nutty and earthy flavor.

00:04:36.080 --> 00:04:38.376
It can be turned into salad,

00:04:38.400 --> 00:04:40.496
served as noodles,

00:04:40.520 --> 00:04:42.136
used in baking

00:04:42.160 --> 00:04:47.856
or simply as a substitute for any
other grains in your favorite recipes.

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:54.256
I am happy to share some of my
fonio sushi and sweet potato sushi

00:04:54.280 --> 00:04:55.640
with some of you right now.

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.296
(Audience) Oh!

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.816
(Applause)